'''''KronoScope''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] dedicated to the interdisciplinary study of [[time]], both in the [[humanities]] and in the [[sciences]]. It is published biannually under the imprint of [[Brill Publishers]] on behalf of the [[International Society for the Study of Time]]. It is indexed in [[Sociological Abstracts]].<ref name=Brill>{{cite web |url=http://www.brill.com/kronoscope|title=KronoScope - BRILL |format= |work= |accessdate=2015-04-30}}</ref>
